data.description: Brentwood Charmer! This fully remodeled 3 bedroom home hosts an array of magnificent features. You have got to see it to believe it! Designer paint throughout, stainless steel appliances, new wood stove, tiled bathtub surround, large attached one-car garage, open floor plan, and much more! Convenient location, situated on a quiet neighborhood street with ample amount of parking. Soon you will be calling this place your home!!!
